Bootstrap- also called as the mobile first approach
-->Framework of CSS
-->convinent of styling
-->pre-defined set of style

Ways to achieve the BS styling:-
1. -->Using CDN[Content Delivery Network]--online method
2. -->Downloading the Bootstrap files-->extract the files-->"bootstrap.min.css" and "bootstrap.css" openwith VScode
      [.min.css has less file size comparatively so the updation of the web pages or opening of the webpages is faster]
3. -->using npm commands[use of Node.js]

