container:- provides left and right margin
--> class="container"
container-fluid:- occupies the 100% width
--> class="container-fluid"
***fullscreen container is applied if we shrink it furhter, then after some value of the screen size
   it will become container-fluid
--> class="container-lg"[for lg, xl, and xxl devices it will act as container 
    if it is below lg then it will act as container-fluid ]   

