Margin:-
  mt-[num]--> margin top 
  mb-[num]--> margin bottom   
  ms-[num]--> margin left
  me-[num]--> margin right
  mx-[num]--> margin left and right
  my-[num]--> margin top and bottom
  m-[num] --> margin on all sides

Padding:-
  pt-[num]--> padding top  
  pb-[num]--> padding bottom 
  ps-[num]--> padding left 
  pe-[num]--> padding right 
  px-[num]--> padding left and right  
  py-[num]--> padding top and bottom 
  p-[num] --> padding on all sides 

